ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENTS:

When using or redistributing this template, you must:

1. Give appropriate credit to the original author (AshDevFr)
2. Provide a link to the original repository:
   https://github.com/AshDevFr/latex-cookbook-template
3. Provide a link to the license:
   https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/
4. Indicate if any modifications were made to the original template
5. If you create a modified version, you must license it under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0

Example attribution text:
"This cookbook uses the LaTeX Cookbook Template by AshDevFr
(https://github.com/AshDevFr/latex-cookbook-template), licensed under
CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/)."

You may include attribution in your cookbook's colophon, copyright page,
or README file. For digital distributions, a link is sufficient.

